WEBVTT

01:40.410 --> 01:45.930
[Speed and Love]

01:46.289 --> 01:48.830
[Episode 6]

01:53.640 --> 01:54.400
Sanlai,

01:54.670 --> 01:56.729
why are we doing this so late at night?

01:57.430 --> 01:58.509
It's all because that guy Brandy

01:58.509 --> 01:59.640
gave me homework,

02:00.090 --> 02:01.720
making me circle left ten times

02:01.720 --> 02:02.850
and right ten times.

02:03.030 --> 02:05.340
I'm not a donkey.
Why does he keep making me go in circles?

02:05.340 --> 02:06.250
Homework?

02:07.000 --> 02:08.400
What else did he give you?

02:08.440 --> 02:09.500
Can I hear about it?

02:16.480 --> 02:18.070
Turn toward the center,

02:18.560 --> 02:19.620
step on the clutch,

02:20.070 --> 02:21.480
rev the engine hard,

02:22.030 --> 02:24.100
release the clutch quickly
to start the drift,

02:24.100 --> 02:25.380
let the tail swing 90 degrees,

02:25.380 --> 02:26.810
ease off, counter-steer,

02:26.810 --> 02:28.970
immediately hit the gas
to keep it sliding,

02:28.970 --> 02:31.370
and then adjust the steering and throttle.

02:32.280 --> 02:33.680
Did you understand that?

02:34.500 --> 02:35.570
You didn't?

02:36.500 --> 02:38.100
Of course I got it right away.

02:38.690 --> 02:39.490
Let's go then.

02:42.690 --> 02:43.690
Clutch out.

02:49.410 --> 02:51.510
No, wait.
Pull the handbrake and then what?

02:51.510 --> 02:52.940
Never mind. It doesn't matter.

02:52.940 --> 02:53.970
The first step is always the hardest.

02:53.970 --> 02:55.180
We've got the first circle down.

02:55.180 --> 02:55.850
The rest will be easier.

02:55.850 --> 02:56.500
Yes.

02:56.620 --> 02:58.680
Sanlai, you're already doing great.

02:59.620 --> 03:01.810
But… this doesn't look much like a circle.

03:01.810 --> 03:02.810
Doesn't matter.

03:02.900 --> 03:04.300
As long as I got it to spin.

03:05.180 --> 03:06.580
If you want to drift in big circles,

03:06.580 --> 03:08.300
you need to
adjust the steering and throttle

03:08.300 --> 03:10.090
to increase rear-wheel traction

03:10.090 --> 03:11.340
and push the vehicle outward.

03:11.340 --> 03:13.200
You need speed to start drifting.

03:13.220 --> 03:14.670
Clutch in, floor the gas,

03:14.690 --> 03:16.170
then pop the clutch.

03:40.690 --> 03:41.350
This is fun!

03:41.740 --> 03:43.540
Dad, you're so cool! Do it again!

03:43.740 --> 03:44.740
Roller coaster!

03:44.870 --> 03:46.670
See? My daughter takes after me.

03:47.460 --> 03:48.970
Hurry up, Dad! One more time!

03:48.970 --> 03:50.690
Alright! Roller coaster!

03:55.740 --> 03:57.020
Faster, Dad!

03:59.250 --> 04:00.400
If you want to drift in big circles,

04:00.400 --> 04:02.340
you need to
adjust the steering and throttle

04:02.340 --> 04:03.650
to increase rear-wheel traction

04:03.650 --> 04:05.310
and push the vehicle outward.

04:09.750 --> 04:11.640
You seem to have forgotten
to straighten the wheel.

04:11.640 --> 04:14.500
Why did you say exactly the same thing
as Brandy did?

04:16.209 --> 04:17.690
Maybe it's just a coincidence.

04:17.690 --> 04:19.180
Sanlai, try again.

04:19.420 --> 04:20.970
Remember to straighten the wheel
once you start drifting.

04:20.970 --> 04:22.370
And don't forget the gas.

04:23.660 --> 04:24.390
Okay.

04:25.330 --> 04:26.420
I'm going all out.

04:42.050 --> 04:44.290
Sanlai, you forgot to hit the gas.

04:47.130 --> 04:48.330
I want to give it a try.

04:48.690 --> 04:50.400
Well, be careful.

04:50.720 --> 04:52.690
I haven't gotten married and had kids yet.

04:52.690 --> 04:54.480
Don't worry. I know what I'm doing.

04:54.480 --> 04:55.940
I'll get the car out first.

04:59.870 --> 05:00.790
Well...

05:02.450 --> 05:03.810
Just a small mistake.

05:05.370 --> 05:06.970
Have you ever driven before?

05:07.420 --> 05:08.620
I haven't,

05:09.130 --> 05:11.380
but I watched my dad drive a lot
when I was a kid.

05:11.380 --> 05:13.110
Wait. Let me think for a second.

05:13.130 --> 05:13.930
Wait a minute.

05:14.500 --> 05:15.410
Your dad?

05:15.570 --> 05:17.100
Jin Qiang? That alcoholic?

05:17.180 --> 05:17.810
Yes.

05:18.090 --> 05:18.980
When he was young,

05:18.980 --> 05:20.450
he was a great racer.

05:20.950 --> 05:23.010
Are we talking about the same person?

05:30.080 --> 05:31.880
Feel the grip in the rear wheels.

05:41.920 --> 05:44.250
Feel how the gas and brakes work together.

05:56.909 --> 05:57.590
What...

05:59.100 --> 06:00.060
just happened?

06:00.660 --> 06:02.420
I told you. Strong genes.

06:03.250 --> 06:04.330
Family genes.

06:05.910 --> 06:06.500
Alright.

06:06.830 --> 06:07.630
Figure eight.

06:07.970 --> 06:08.580
Let's go.

06:11.540 --> 06:12.950
Brake, brake, brake!

06:16.370 --> 06:17.540
Who drives a car

06:18.220 --> 06:19.540
in reverse anyway?

06:20.180 --> 06:21.780
Just another small mistake.

06:21.800 --> 06:22.600
Let me try again.

06:22.600 --> 06:23.310
Wait!

06:23.890 --> 06:24.950
I'll get out first.

06:25.330 --> 06:26.260
Are you serious?

06:26.690 --> 06:27.620
Sanlai!

06:28.940 --> 06:29.690
Be careful.

06:40.300 --> 06:41.630
Ease off the gas, then push.

06:41.630 --> 06:42.960
Turn the wheel earlier.

06:43.220 --> 06:46.680
Don't wait until the front goes past
before turning the wheel.

06:58.260 --> 06:59.650
You're amazing!

07:00.300 --> 07:01.500
Was that impressive?

07:01.620 --> 07:02.370
Yeah.

07:02.660 --> 07:04.120
Let me show you another trick.

07:04.120 --> 07:04.880
Be careful!

07:15.140 --> 07:15.990
Are you okay?

07:23.250 --> 07:24.010
Nana?

07:24.640 --> 07:25.450
Mu!

07:26.980 --> 07:28.300
Little fortune teller?

07:28.300 --> 07:29.500
You know Jiang Mu too?

07:29.980 --> 07:31.100
We met on the plane.

07:31.160 --> 07:32.490
You two know each other?

07:33.450 --> 07:35.010
She was my childhood sweetheart.

07:35.010 --> 07:35.720
Nonsense!

07:35.740 --> 07:37.870
We were just neighbors for a few years.

07:38.370 --> 07:39.050
Mu,

07:39.550 --> 07:41.860
I signed you up
for a driving school in Manshi.

07:41.860 --> 07:43.320
We can go for lessons soon.

07:43.370 --> 07:44.810
That place is great in every way,

07:44.810 --> 07:45.980
except there are no hot guys.

07:45.980 --> 07:46.570
But tonight,

07:46.570 --> 07:48.250
I can take you somewhere with hot guys.

07:48.250 --> 07:48.860
Let's go!

07:50.370 --> 07:51.100
Get in.

07:51.710 --> 07:54.710
Little fortune teller,
where are you taking Jiang Mu?

07:58.659 --> 07:59.250
Mu,

07:59.320 --> 08:00.620
it's very diverse here.

08:00.620 --> 08:02.480
People speak Thai, Chinese, and English.

08:02.480 --> 08:03.940
And there's one special thing—

08:03.940 --> 08:05.060
because of the modified cars,

08:05.060 --> 08:07.280
left-hand and right-hand drive vehicles
can race together.

08:07.280 --> 08:08.500
Everyone's used to it.

08:08.500 --> 08:10.230
Nobody finds it strange at all.

08:11.650 --> 08:12.910
Let me show you around!

08:15.210 --> 08:16.330
Welcome to

08:16.400 --> 08:19.350
the ultimate vacation destination!

08:20.150 --> 08:21.690
The car modification scene here

08:21.690 --> 08:22.870
is absolutely thriving.

08:22.870 --> 08:24.190
As long as a car meets basic standards,

08:24.190 --> 08:25.500
it can be legally on the road.

08:25.500 --> 08:27.420
I categorize them into three groups:

08:27.420 --> 08:29.100
performance,

08:29.210 --> 08:31.620
show, and supercars.

08:32.370 --> 08:33.490
I know supercars.

08:33.570 --> 08:34.659
What are the other two?

08:34.659 --> 08:35.659
Performance cars

08:35.690 --> 08:37.330
aren't about looks.

08:37.659 --> 08:39.780
They may look ordinary,

08:39.850 --> 08:42.299
but they have huge modification potential

08:42.299 --> 08:43.020
and handle really well.

08:43.020 --> 08:44.179
People who drive these cars

08:44.179 --> 08:45.610
are all thrill-seekers.

08:45.780 --> 08:47.060
On the track,

08:47.300 --> 08:49.490
they go all out, risking their lives.

08:49.690 --> 08:51.610
There are often straight-line drag races.

08:51.610 --> 08:53.140
My cousin is into this type.

08:55.260 --> 08:57.060
The show cars are over here.

08:57.420 --> 08:59.330
They look extremely gorgeous,

08:59.450 --> 09:01.100
with custom paint and fancy rims,

09:01.100 --> 09:03.160
but they're all show and no go—

09:03.300 --> 09:04.850
just good for taking pictures,
not much else.

09:04.850 --> 09:06.970
I personally prefer

09:07.090 --> 09:08.400
the supercars.

09:09.730 --> 09:11.060
Look at this sleek line.

09:11.490 --> 09:12.970
They've got the looks,

09:13.060 --> 09:14.260
they've got the performance,

09:14.260 --> 09:16.190
and they're the complete package.

09:22.620 --> 09:23.950
Here comes a muscle car.

09:26.570 --> 09:29.490
Check out this exhaust
and listen to that roar.

09:29.780 --> 09:31.490
It makes you want to step on the gas—

09:31.490 --> 09:32.750
like riding on clouds.

09:33.450 --> 09:35.250
But I'm not really into this car.

09:35.450 --> 09:36.900
I think it's a bit too bulky.

09:36.900 --> 09:38.360
I still prefer supercars.

09:51.370 --> 09:52.100
Sanlai!

09:55.260 --> 09:56.260
Where's Jiang Mu?

09:56.450 --> 09:57.650
You know Nana, right?

09:58.250 --> 10:01.330
The little fortune teller
who read fortunes for Wan Qing?

10:01.330 --> 10:01.900
Yes.

10:02.090 --> 10:02.730
Jiang Mu said

10:02.730 --> 10:04.140
they met on the plane.

10:04.260 --> 10:06.590
And tonight,
Nana took her out to have fun.

10:13.860 --> 10:16.030
[Jin Zhao]

10:19.380 --> 10:20.180
What's wrong?

10:20.340 --> 10:22.070
She's not answering her phone.

10:29.380 --> 10:30.330
A hot guy.

10:32.490 --> 10:34.490
Don't you think he's sexy?

10:36.690 --> 10:38.450
Isn't your guy that type?

10:38.780 --> 10:39.660
My guy?

10:40.040 --> 10:41.250
The one called...

10:43.930 --> 10:44.690
Jin Zhao.

10:46.180 --> 10:47.450
He's not that type.

10:47.690 --> 10:48.890
He's quite arrogant.

10:50.180 --> 10:51.970
Mr. Attitude, huh?

10:52.130 --> 10:54.380
Tell me the details.
I want to hear everything.

10:54.380 --> 10:55.380
Actually...

10:57.970 --> 11:00.610
he usually seems pretty normal.

11:00.900 --> 11:01.940
But today

11:02.210 --> 11:04.470
he suddenly did something very strange.

11:04.690 --> 11:06.260
He gave me a...

11:09.660 --> 11:10.570
A what?

11:10.840 --> 11:12.500
Why are you being so hesitant?

11:21.060 --> 11:22.650
That wasn't meant for you, right?

11:22.650 --> 11:24.900
I think so. It was probably a mistake.

11:27.090 --> 11:28.540
Could it be…

11:28.800 --> 11:30.480
he has another woman?

11:32.900 --> 11:34.500
I've thought about that too.

11:35.210 --> 11:37.440
I wanted to ask him,

11:37.800 --> 11:39.800
but I was afraid it would be awkward.

11:40.610 --> 11:41.490
Sometimes

11:41.660 --> 11:43.370
I wish he would think a little more

11:43.370 --> 11:45.300
and not just see me as a sister.

11:45.650 --> 11:47.690
But I'm also afraid he'll overthink it.

11:47.690 --> 11:49.180
If he rejects me,

11:49.500 --> 11:51.760
I won't even get to be his sister anymore.

11:53.020 --> 11:54.380
It's so complicated.

11:55.570 --> 11:56.780
You can't just ask him directly.

11:56.780 --> 11:57.610
Right.

11:57.610 --> 12:00.300
But you can test him indirectly.

12:00.420 --> 12:01.140
How?

12:02.140 --> 12:03.300
Make him think

12:03.610 --> 12:05.020
you have another man.

12:06.690 --> 12:07.570
Isn't that a little inappropriate?

12:07.570 --> 12:09.210
What's inappropriate about it?

12:09.210 --> 12:09.970
Listen to me.

12:10.180 --> 12:11.240
This is the only way

12:11.260 --> 12:12.420
you can find out

12:12.540 --> 12:14.140
whether he even has

12:14.300 --> 12:16.780
the slightest bit of feeling for you.

12:19.900 --> 12:20.850
It sounds...

12:20.970 --> 12:22.330
like a good idea.

12:22.370 --> 12:23.090
Exactly.

12:23.090 --> 12:24.890
Where am I supposed to find a guy?

12:25.330 --> 12:26.660
Use what's available.

12:26.870 --> 12:28.600
There are so many hot guys here.

12:29.270 --> 12:30.620
[Where have you been?]

12:31.970 --> 12:32.810
Is it him?

12:33.060 --> 12:35.310
[Why didn't you pick up?]

12:38.330 --> 12:39.460
Don't call him back.

12:39.740 --> 12:40.740
Keep him waiting.

12:41.730 --> 12:43.450
There's an old saying in China:

12:43.450 --> 12:45.230
"You can't make a deal
by lowering yourself."

12:45.230 --> 12:47.390
You can't always be the proactive one.

12:47.690 --> 12:49.060
You need to provoke him a little

12:49.060 --> 12:49.940
and take back

12:49.940 --> 12:51.610
the initiative.

12:56.850 --> 12:58.570
Don't be afraid of using old tricks.

12:58.570 --> 13:00.210
Old tricks work best.

13:00.810 --> 13:01.490
Really.

13:01.810 --> 13:03.260
Now we just need a guy

13:03.260 --> 13:04.730
competitive enough

13:04.900 --> 13:06.810
to do us this tiny favor.

13:08.190 --> 13:10.420
Competitive?

13:17.440 --> 13:18.520
Not Liang Yanfeng.

13:18.830 --> 13:19.900
He's a well-known playboy

13:19.900 --> 13:21.450
in this circle.

13:21.480 --> 13:22.840
Stay away from him.

13:23.900 --> 13:25.090
But from what I've seen,

13:25.090 --> 13:27.750
he's the only one
who looks competitive enough.

13:28.610 --> 13:30.470
There's someone better than him.

13:35.580 --> 13:36.580
Here he comes.

13:39.200 --> 13:41.120
My cousin, the host tonight,

13:41.330 --> 13:42.810
and the birthday boy.

13:43.900 --> 13:45.540
-Cousin?
-It's him.

13:46.700 --> 13:47.230
Let's go.

13:47.470 --> 13:48.800
I'll take you to see him.

13:49.140 --> 13:50.380
Here comes the birthday boy.

13:50.380 --> 13:51.310
Happy birthday.

13:52.180 --> 13:53.510
You're more excited than I am.

13:53.510 --> 13:55.110
Well, you're my good friend.

13:55.540 --> 13:57.670
When have I ever missed your birthday?

13:57.780 --> 13:59.910
Looks to me like you're here for girls.

14:00.590 --> 14:02.110
Men are like race cars.

14:02.330 --> 14:05.860
If you're picking one,
pick the one that stands out in every way.

14:06.120 --> 14:08.120
Your cousin looks like a foreigner.

14:08.250 --> 14:09.250
Is he mixed-race?

14:09.420 --> 14:11.570
No, pure local.

14:11.900 --> 14:13.020
But you're in luck.

14:13.050 --> 14:14.980
He speaks Chinese fluently.

14:15.300 --> 14:16.010
And...

14:16.170 --> 14:17.780
he likes Chinese girls.

14:19.310 --> 14:20.830
But he looks like a bad guy.

14:21.640 --> 14:22.520
No, no, no.

14:23.180 --> 14:24.690
He's never had any

14:24.690 --> 14:26.260
questionable women around him.

14:26.260 --> 14:27.640
The flirty types in this circle

14:27.640 --> 14:29.130
never catch his eye.

14:30.450 --> 14:33.420
My girlfriends and I always gossip,

14:33.610 --> 14:35.300
saying he's either...

14:36.850 --> 14:38.940
Or secretly in love

14:39.090 --> 14:41.450
with a mysterious, sexy Chinese woman.

14:41.570 --> 14:43.060
Why a Chinese woman?

14:43.380 --> 14:45.730
How else would he speak Chinese so well?

14:46.170 --> 14:48.300
The biggest motivation to learn a language

14:48.300 --> 14:49.850
is romance.

14:52.420 --> 14:54.420
Alright. Go over there and have fun.

14:54.540 --> 14:56.180
Later, when I give you a push,

14:56.330 --> 14:57.590
stand on your tiptoes.

14:57.970 --> 14:58.540
I'm scared.

14:58.540 --> 15:00.140
It's fine. Just listen to me.

15:00.300 --> 15:01.420
Trust me, okay?

15:01.620 --> 15:02.450
Wait a second.

15:05.340 --> 15:06.580
Sui!

15:09.800 --> 15:10.310
Go!

15:15.990 --> 15:17.050
Sui!

15:17.130 --> 15:19.490
Your hairstyle
looks especially cool today.

15:19.490 --> 15:20.970
I just took a photo as a reference

15:20.970 --> 15:22.370
to show my brother later.

15:22.420 --> 15:23.420
Tonight,

15:23.910 --> 15:25.390
don't touch my car.

15:27.230 --> 15:28.900
Don't worry. Tonight...

15:29.240 --> 15:30.370
I have another plan.

15:37.330 --> 15:38.730
Let's check the results.

15:39.330 --> 15:41.130
Look at my cousin's gaze.

15:41.540 --> 15:42.730
A woman can fall in love with him

15:42.730 --> 15:44.490
just by looking at him.

15:44.970 --> 15:47.970
It's electrifying,
naturally full of sexual tension.

15:47.970 --> 15:50.070
Your curves aren't bad either.

15:50.090 --> 15:52.220
It's a young woman's greatest allure.

15:52.810 --> 15:53.870
It's okay, I guess.

15:54.000 --> 15:55.570
This photo looks pretty ordinary.

15:55.570 --> 15:56.780
How can you tell?

15:57.810 --> 15:59.660
I'm sending you this photo now.

15:59.900 --> 16:00.970
Send it to Jin Zhao.

16:01.140 --> 16:02.280
Right away. Immediately.

16:02.280 --> 16:02.850
Hurry!

16:06.070 --> 16:06.970
What should I say?

16:06.970 --> 16:07.930
Don't say anything.

16:07.930 --> 16:09.410
Just send it to him,

16:10.090 --> 16:11.420
then send our location,

16:11.730 --> 16:12.520
then...

16:12.940 --> 16:14.210
turn off your phone.

16:14.970 --> 16:16.290
Isn't that a bit manipulative?

16:16.290 --> 16:18.490
You might as well go full manipulative.

16:18.730 --> 16:20.140
Ten seconds after sending it,

16:20.140 --> 16:21.220
recall it.

16:24.220 --> 16:25.380
Then write,

16:25.900 --> 16:27.520
"Sent by mistake. My hand slipped."

16:27.520 --> 16:28.450
"Don't mind me."

16:29.260 --> 16:30.710
You're a quick learner!

16:37.180 --> 16:39.650
Now, all we need to do is...

16:40.210 --> 16:41.130
wait.

16:43.020 --> 16:44.480
I've sorted it out for you.

16:44.810 --> 16:46.140
That thing you wanted—

16:46.280 --> 16:47.480
Zhang Guangyu has it.

16:48.500 --> 16:50.090
The gathering is at 9 PM tonight.

16:50.090 --> 16:51.120
Are you on your way?

16:51.120 --> 16:52.450
I'm not coming tonight.

16:53.210 --> 16:54.610
Yeah, something came up.

16:54.810 --> 16:56.070
Okay, I'll hang up now.

17:09.490 --> 17:10.290
I'm sorry.

17:10.380 --> 17:11.660
My hand slipped. Sent by mistake.

17:11.660 --> 17:12.530
Don't mind me.

17:14.290 --> 17:15.550
Send me Nana's number.

17:29.590 --> 17:30.460
Miss Nana...

17:34.490 --> 17:35.250
Oh no.

17:35.620 --> 17:37.990
That woman's henchmen
are here to catch me again.

17:37.990 --> 17:38.900
Don't look!

17:39.050 --> 17:39.960
Face this way.

17:40.450 --> 17:40.970
Let's do this.

17:40.970 --> 17:42.300
Mu, wait for me a minute.

17:42.530 --> 17:44.330
Let's meet in the living room later.

17:44.330 --> 17:45.730
I'll draw him away first.

17:45.900 --> 17:47.290
See you in 10 minutes.

18:12.670 --> 18:13.670
Hello.

18:14.340 --> 18:15.420
Hello.

18:15.990 --> 18:17.850
So you're really Brandy's woman?

18:22.010 --> 18:23.050
Guess not.

18:23.660 --> 18:24.970
That night at the warehouse,

18:24.970 --> 18:26.210
Brandy lied.

18:26.770 --> 18:28.530
If the people in the alliance find out,

18:28.530 --> 18:29.860
he'll be in big trouble.

18:33.010 --> 18:34.940
How much do you know about Brandy?

18:37.380 --> 18:38.840
What are you trying to say?

18:39.450 --> 18:41.780
Clearly you're interested in this topic.

18:44.410 --> 18:45.650
If I tell you

18:46.410 --> 18:48.260
I know a lot of his secrets,

18:49.120 --> 18:51.380
would you be interested in talking to me?

18:56.790 --> 18:57.590
Hello.

19:08.530 --> 19:09.210
What?

19:09.620 --> 19:10.630
Afraid to drink it?

19:10.630 --> 19:12.630
Are you afraid I put something in it?

19:13.500 --> 19:14.380
You were quite bold

19:14.380 --> 19:16.050
at the warehouse that night.

19:31.770 --> 19:33.640
I've drunk it. You can tell me now.

19:34.130 --> 19:35.160
How interesting.

19:35.620 --> 19:37.610
How could Snakey allow someone like you

19:37.610 --> 19:38.860
to stay around Brandy?

19:38.860 --> 19:39.970
Who's Snakey?

19:40.100 --> 19:40.820
What?

19:41.100 --> 19:42.430
You haven't met her yet?

20:41.290 --> 20:41.970
Hello.

20:42.310 --> 20:43.110
I'm Jin Zhao.

20:44.090 --> 20:44.890
Jin Zhao.

20:46.860 --> 20:47.580
Jin Zhao?

20:47.730 --> 20:49.190
Give the phone to Jiang Mu.

20:53.280 --> 20:53.860
Miss Nana!

20:53.860 --> 20:54.820
-Wait.
-Miss Nana.

20:54.820 --> 20:55.530
Let go of me!

20:55.560 --> 20:56.420
-I finally…
-Help!

20:56.420 --> 20:57.180
Miss Nana, please listen to me.

20:57.180 --> 20:57.970
Let go of me!

20:57.970 --> 20:59.340
Qing is looking for you.
She's been calling you.

20:59.340 --> 21:00.860
I'm not going! I said I'm not going!

21:00.860 --> 21:03.390
-Come with me, Miss Nana.
-What are you doing?

21:04.180 --> 21:04.690
Well...

21:04.820 --> 21:05.930
Brandy, why are you here?

21:05.930 --> 21:07.190
None of your business.

21:07.420 --> 21:08.010
Come on, I'm just...

21:08.010 --> 21:08.860
Get lost.

21:13.410 --> 21:15.140
Remember to answer your phone.

21:16.170 --> 21:16.820
Let's go.

21:19.380 --> 21:20.380
Where's Jiang Mu?

21:20.420 --> 21:21.580
You're Jin Zhao, right?

21:21.580 --> 21:23.180
I asked you where Jiang Mu is.

21:23.400 --> 21:24.400
Come with me.

21:30.620 --> 21:31.290
Who is this?

21:31.580 --> 21:32.410
Nana's friend.

21:32.410 --> 21:34.770
She might have drunk something
that was drugged.

21:34.770 --> 21:36.180
I'll notify Miss Nana right away.

21:36.180 --> 21:37.290
Should I call an ambulance?

21:37.290 --> 21:37.770
No need.

21:37.910 --> 21:39.050
Get me a glass of milk first.

21:39.050 --> 21:40.180
To induce vomiting?

21:40.400 --> 21:41.330
She only took one sip.

21:41.330 --> 21:42.160
It shouldn't be serious.

21:42.160 --> 21:44.020
Okay, I'll prepare it right away.

21:57.980 --> 21:58.660
Move!

22:01.380 --> 22:02.100
Mu.

22:03.160 --> 22:04.810
Mu, what happened to you? Mu?

22:05.130 --> 22:06.490
Were you drugged?

22:06.580 --> 22:08.740
Was it a sedative or something else, Mu?

22:08.740 --> 22:10.260
Mu? Mu?

22:10.660 --> 22:11.620
Bastard.

22:15.160 --> 22:16.290
What did you say?

22:16.820 --> 22:18.150
I said you're a bastard.

22:24.210 --> 22:26.050
Stop fighting!

22:31.030 --> 22:33.340
Stop it! Stop fighting!

22:35.220 --> 22:37.420
I couldn't stand you
that day at the boxing gym.

22:37.420 --> 22:38.660
You have the nerve to say that?

22:38.660 --> 22:39.970
You ran away in the middle of the fight.

22:39.970 --> 22:41.790
I haven't settled the score with you yet.

22:41.790 --> 22:43.390
Come on, let's settle it now.

23:03.540 --> 23:04.890
I hate cream the most.

23:06.710 --> 23:07.800
Sorry.

23:09.860 --> 23:11.790
I'll try something else next time.

23:12.560 --> 23:14.320
Sui, stop fighting.

23:50.690 --> 23:51.650
Nana...

23:52.350 --> 23:53.830
Mu, you're awake?

23:55.480 --> 23:56.730
Stop fighting, you two!

23:56.730 --> 23:58.490
Come over! Mu's awake!

23:59.840 --> 24:00.520
Mu!

24:10.600 --> 24:11.470
Are you okay?

24:15.940 --> 24:17.050
You got hurt?

24:18.010 --> 24:19.770
He thought my cousin spiked your drink,

24:19.770 --> 24:20.770
so he hit him.

24:20.900 --> 24:22.940
Actually,
the two of them started fighting.

24:22.940 --> 24:24.790
It was quite a show.

24:27.690 --> 24:28.580
I just remember

24:28.690 --> 24:30.250
having a cocktail,

24:31.620 --> 24:33.140
then I felt dizzy

24:33.820 --> 24:34.780
and nauseous.

24:36.620 --> 24:38.210
My skin still itches.

25:06.870 --> 25:08.930
You're having an allergic reaction.

25:09.600 --> 25:10.660
Did you eat a peach?

25:12.970 --> 25:13.900
I think so.

25:14.450 --> 25:15.420
That cocktail

25:15.420 --> 25:17.450
tasted like peach.

25:19.930 --> 25:21.590
I'll take you to the hospital.

25:30.590 --> 25:32.520
I'll return the favor another day.

25:37.970 --> 25:39.430
How's it now? Still itchy?

25:39.820 --> 25:40.620
Really?

25:42.090 --> 25:42.960
He's coming.

25:51.690 --> 25:53.100
Is he always this quiet?

25:55.490 --> 25:57.290
Maybe he's angry because he thinks

25:57.290 --> 25:58.690
I caused trouble for him.

25:59.810 --> 26:01.000
Here you go.

26:01.490 --> 26:02.970
This is how you should be.

26:03.280 --> 26:05.010
You can't be too well-behaved.

26:05.100 --> 26:06.660
You need to cause him some trouble

26:06.660 --> 26:07.970
every now and then.

26:08.380 --> 26:09.340
That way,

26:09.340 --> 26:10.730
you stay on his radar.

26:11.490 --> 26:12.550
Is that necessary?

26:13.130 --> 26:14.050
Of course.

26:22.080 --> 26:24.140
He knows you're allergic to peaches?

26:26.060 --> 26:28.260
Haven't you two been apart for 10 years?

26:28.650 --> 26:29.370
Yes.

26:30.080 --> 26:32.480
And he still remembers your peach allergy?

26:35.970 --> 26:37.450
That means

26:37.890 --> 26:40.200
he's been thinking of you all this time.

26:44.300 --> 26:47.030
Looks like tonight's little test
wasn't wasted.

27:00.820 --> 27:01.580
How is she?

27:01.820 --> 27:02.970
Nothing serious.

27:03.210 --> 27:04.460
I've prescribed some allergy medication.

27:04.460 --> 27:05.860
Just take it as directed.

27:06.140 --> 27:07.560
He says there's nothing too serious.

27:07.560 --> 27:08.530
He's prescribed some allergy medication.

27:08.530 --> 27:09.690
Just take it at home and you'll be fine.

27:09.690 --> 27:12.450
But she needs to stay
in the hospital tonight for observation.

27:12.450 --> 27:13.560
But tonight,

27:13.580 --> 27:15.770
you need to stay in the hospital
for observation.

27:15.770 --> 27:16.490
By the way,

27:16.650 --> 27:19.250
the patient shows some signs
of malnutrition.

27:23.010 --> 27:23.870
What did he say?

27:23.970 --> 27:25.450
He said you're a bit...

27:25.660 --> 27:26.530
malnourished.

27:28.100 --> 27:30.030
What kind of brother are you to her?

27:30.030 --> 27:31.090
She's only been at your place a few days

27:31.090 --> 27:32.410
and already malnourished.

27:32.410 --> 27:34.070
Have you been neglecting her?

27:34.080 --> 27:35.410
It's not because of him.

27:35.730 --> 27:37.010
It's just that a lot has happened

27:37.010 --> 27:38.690
these past few days.

27:39.160 --> 27:40.090
I'm exhausted.

27:40.820 --> 27:42.450
Then you must rest properly

27:42.450 --> 27:43.450
in the hospital today.

27:43.450 --> 27:44.940
Family member, come here.

27:45.120 --> 27:46.840
Take this to the front desk to check in.

27:46.840 --> 27:47.990
Play it by ear later.

28:00.760 --> 28:02.990
Have some fruit and get some rest.

28:03.010 --> 28:04.210
Thank you, Nana.

28:06.390 --> 28:06.990
By the way,

28:07.250 --> 28:08.970
I need to go back and tutor my brother.

28:08.970 --> 28:09.500
You know,

28:09.520 --> 28:10.420
he just started high school,

28:10.420 --> 28:11.250
and his grades are at the bottom.

28:11.250 --> 28:13.180
He really can't manage without me. Bye.

28:13.180 --> 28:14.710
I'm leaving Mu in your care.

28:36.540 --> 28:37.540
I won't scold you.

28:43.580 --> 28:44.970
First, act pitiful,

28:45.180 --> 28:46.050
play weak,

28:46.320 --> 28:47.920
and apologize proactively.

28:49.930 --> 28:51.330
I'm sorry about tonight.

28:51.540 --> 28:52.820
I made you worry.

28:57.260 --> 28:59.720
It's nothing.
Let's not talk about that now.

28:59.740 --> 29:01.340
Here, have some water first.

29:06.730 --> 29:09.060
Why hasn't he asked me
about the photo yet?

29:13.300 --> 29:14.210
Well...

29:14.620 --> 29:17.280
It was that guy named Lin Sui
who saved me, right?

29:17.340 --> 29:18.320
You know each other?

29:18.320 --> 29:19.080
Yes, we do.

29:19.380 --> 29:20.580
He's Nana's cousin.

29:20.680 --> 29:22.410
He's quite handsome, isn't he?

29:33.090 --> 29:35.090
Don't you have any questions for me?

29:35.660 --> 29:36.900
Questions about what?

29:36.900 --> 29:37.940
Anything

29:38.770 --> 29:39.890
you want to ask.

29:46.420 --> 29:47.050
Forget it.

29:47.340 --> 29:48.870
Ask or don't ask, whatever.

29:53.950 --> 29:54.810
Are you hungry?

29:55.340 --> 29:56.600
What do you want to eat?

29:57.030 --> 29:58.690
What kind of question is that?

29:59.380 --> 30:01.840
It's so late.
Who would have an appetite now?

30:02.350 --> 30:03.310
I'll call Sanlai

30:03.620 --> 30:04.950
to get some food for you.

30:06.730 --> 30:08.390
Actually, I'm quite healthy.

30:08.580 --> 30:10.710
I eat and sleep well. I'm very healthy.

30:11.140 --> 30:13.380
I've just been a bit busy
these past few days.

30:13.380 --> 30:14.100
I know.

30:14.690 --> 30:15.490
It's my fault.

30:15.730 --> 30:16.860
It's not your fault.

30:17.690 --> 30:19.060
That's not what I meant.

30:21.450 --> 30:23.050
Get some rest early tonight.

30:25.170 --> 30:27.500
This is my first time being hospitalized.

30:30.620 --> 30:31.620
I'm a bit scared.

30:48.770 --> 30:49.830
I'll stay with you.

30:50.930 --> 30:52.650
You'll stay here all night?

31:01.820 --> 31:03.010
Sanlai said...

31:03.730 --> 31:05.730
you went out of town to meet someone.

31:11.700 --> 31:12.870
Did you go alone?

31:13.520 --> 31:14.360
Yes, alone.

31:16.620 --> 31:17.690
Don't be afraid to ask.

31:17.690 --> 31:19.620
You need to make him face the storm.

31:19.620 --> 31:22.600
The more you avoid it, the harder it is
to see his true attitude.

31:22.600 --> 31:24.000
Did you go to meet a woman?

31:30.350 --> 31:31.410
Why do you ask that?

31:33.770 --> 31:35.430
Did someone give you trouble?

31:36.670 --> 31:37.990
No one gave me trouble.

31:41.770 --> 31:43.500
I just don't want to bother you.

31:44.470 --> 31:45.430
Bother me how?

31:47.770 --> 31:48.660
Like tonight.

31:48.860 --> 31:50.620
You have to stay here to take care of me.

31:50.620 --> 31:52.150
What if someone gets upset?

32:07.910 --> 32:09.190
I went to meet a man.

32:11.560 --> 32:12.620
There was no woman.

32:15.350 --> 32:16.700
And no one will be upset.

32:20.890 --> 32:21.930
Unless...

32:26.500 --> 32:27.550
you're upset.

32:29.090 --> 32:31.000
Not at all. I'm very happy.

32:38.760 --> 32:40.330
I suddenly have an appetite.

32:40.330 --> 32:41.810
I want an apple.

32:49.320 --> 32:50.110
Brandy.

32:53.860 --> 32:55.120
What are you two doing?

32:56.740 --> 32:58.000
What are you two doing?

32:59.890 --> 33:02.090
Stop yelling in the middle of the night.

33:02.580 --> 33:04.430
What are you waiting for?
Put them over there.

33:04.430 --> 33:06.050
You called me over here
to run errands at this hour,

33:06.050 --> 33:07.730
and you didn't even say thank you.

33:07.730 --> 33:09.290
If it weren't for Jiang Mu's health,

33:09.290 --> 33:10.820
I wouldn't bother with you.

33:11.450 --> 33:12.900
So? Are you alright?

33:13.010 --> 33:14.100
How's your recovery going?

33:14.100 --> 33:15.730
I didn't even know
you were allergic to peaches.

33:15.730 --> 33:17.190
Stop babbling and get out.

33:17.380 --> 33:18.710
Don't disturb her rest.

33:19.040 --> 33:19.720
Me?

33:20.590 --> 33:21.380
Disturb?

33:26.070 --> 33:26.830
Come out.

33:27.970 --> 33:30.030
I need to talk to you about something.

33:30.240 --> 33:30.840
Come out.

33:35.290 --> 33:36.160
What is it?

33:40.250 --> 33:41.210
Look at me with those eyes again,

33:41.210 --> 33:43.070
and I'll gouge your eyeballs out.

33:43.690 --> 33:45.290
What were you doing just now?

33:47.250 --> 33:48.100
When?

33:51.690 --> 33:53.020
I was getting the apple.

33:54.210 --> 33:55.050
The apple?

33:58.240 --> 33:59.500
The apple smells nice.

34:04.970 --> 34:05.940
Jiang Mu

34:06.630 --> 34:07.490
asked me today

34:07.490 --> 34:08.889
if you have a girlfriend.

34:09.650 --> 34:10.580
What did you say?

34:11.739 --> 34:12.670
I told her you do.

34:14.360 --> 34:15.820
But it's not official yet.

34:17.219 --> 34:18.420
Come on. You could've just told the truth
and said I don't.

34:18.420 --> 34:20.679
Why did you say something so misleading?

34:20.699 --> 34:23.860
I thought it through very carefully.

34:24.570 --> 34:26.230
I felt that was the only answer

34:27.219 --> 34:28.949
my conscience could live with.

34:29.380 --> 34:30.980
Keep causing trouble for me.

34:32.690 --> 34:33.340
You eat it.

34:35.650 --> 34:37.510
You don't need the apple anymore?

34:41.730 --> 34:42.290
Nana,

34:42.409 --> 34:43.860
let me tell you, he...

34:48.420 --> 34:49.350
Where's Sanlai?

34:51.050 --> 34:52.050
I chased him away.

34:54.699 --> 34:56.230
Do you still want the apple?

35:07.660 --> 35:09.990
What were you two talking about out there?

35:10.340 --> 35:11.090
Nothing.

35:35.450 --> 35:36.260
I...

35:39.690 --> 35:41.150
I don't have a girlfriend,

35:45.310 --> 35:47.640
and I'm not thinking about that right now.

35:49.300 --> 35:51.500
You don't need to worry about anything.

35:54.820 --> 35:56.220
Since you're here,

35:58.420 --> 35:59.950
besides Jin Qiang's place,

36:01.490 --> 36:02.750
mine is also your home.

36:06.870 --> 36:07.730
With me around,

36:09.420 --> 36:10.570
no one can bully you.

36:24.670 --> 36:26.790
Excuse me. I'm doing my rounds.

36:28.210 --> 36:29.370
Sign here please.

36:39.940 --> 36:40.940
Sorry about that.

36:52.940 --> 36:54.010
Isn't this the gift I gave him

36:54.010 --> 36:55.340
when I first got here?

36:56.120 --> 36:57.920
He actually carries it with him?

37:04.240 --> 37:05.910
Alright, get some good rest.

37:08.050 --> 37:09.450
I'm not leaving tonight.

37:09.530 --> 37:11.010
I'll be on the bench outside the door.

37:11.010 --> 37:12.610
Call me if you need anything.

37:15.780 --> 37:17.380
What are you grinning about?

37:49.030 --> 37:50.430
Have some fruit.

37:55.020 --> 37:57.710
I didn't expect Mu's issue
to be a peach allergy.

37:58.450 --> 37:59.940
Good thing the doctor said she's fine

37:59.940 --> 38:01.800
and just needs some allergy meds.

38:02.860 --> 38:04.220
That fight you got into

38:04.680 --> 38:06.070
was quite unnecessary.

38:06.700 --> 38:08.180
You know that girl well?

38:08.700 --> 38:10.100
I'd never met her before.

38:11.220 --> 38:12.920
I met Mu on the plane.

38:13.010 --> 38:15.530
She's super nice, and I really like her.

38:16.570 --> 38:18.700
Don't you dare cause them any trouble.

38:22.570 --> 38:24.650
Don't you have something to say to me?

38:26.900 --> 38:28.340
I'm sorry, Sui.

38:29.130 --> 38:31.170
Today is my birthday.

38:32.860 --> 38:34.780
Happy birthday, Sui.

38:35.170 --> 38:37.530
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

38:37.940 --> 38:40.300
♪ Happy birthday to dear Lin Sui ♪

38:40.450 --> 38:42.340
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

38:51.660 --> 38:53.220
Mu had a mild allergic reaction.

38:53.220 --> 38:54.220
It's not serious.

38:54.470 --> 38:55.130
I'm staying with her.

38:55.130 --> 38:55.930
What's wrong?

38:56.680 --> 38:57.470
Who is it?

39:00.260 --> 39:02.010
She's having an allergic reaction?

39:02.010 --> 39:05.080
Mu has never been able
to eat peaches since she was little.

39:05.080 --> 39:06.600
She's prone to allergies.

39:10.040 --> 39:11.640
Should we go to the hospital?

39:12.050 --> 39:12.970
No need.

39:13.090 --> 39:14.610
Jin Zhao is with her.

39:14.890 --> 39:16.750
Mu will feel more at ease that way.

39:33.900 --> 39:35.350
Can I go to your place?

39:36.570 --> 39:37.570
What do you think?

39:37.610 --> 39:39.260
Didn't you say last night

39:39.860 --> 39:41.010
that besides my dad's place,

39:41.010 --> 39:42.490
yours is also my home?

39:44.820 --> 39:45.970
Let's go to Jin Qiang's first.

39:45.970 --> 39:47.570
Let's go to your place first.

39:59.680 --> 40:01.170
Why are you one person at night

40:01.170 --> 40:02.610
and another during the day?

40:02.610 --> 40:04.420
At night you're so gentle with me,

40:04.420 --> 40:05.530
but during the day

40:05.530 --> 40:07.660
you're cold and impossible to talk to.

40:08.900 --> 40:10.630
You can't say things like that.

40:10.900 --> 40:12.180
People might misunderstand.

40:12.180 --> 40:13.710
I'm just telling the truth.

40:14.200 --> 40:15.860
Let's go to Jin Qiang's first.

40:20.240 --> 40:21.590
If I go to Dad's place

40:22.380 --> 40:25.220
and he sees me looking undernourished,

40:25.740 --> 40:27.570
he'll start worrying again.

40:36.380 --> 40:37.490
Besides,

40:38.110 --> 40:40.240
he gets drunk every night.

40:40.700 --> 40:42.650
He can't even take care of himself,

40:43.400 --> 40:45.480
let alone me.

40:46.210 --> 40:48.810
Mrs. Zhao and I aren't related by blood.

40:49.050 --> 40:51.380
She's not my birth mom.

40:52.610 --> 40:54.450
Jin Xin is so young.

40:55.170 --> 40:57.530
Mrs. Zhao gives all her attention to her.

40:57.780 --> 41:00.180
How could she have energy
to take care of me?

41:01.570 --> 41:02.930
If I go back,

41:03.130 --> 41:06.220
I won't eat well or sleep well.

41:06.610 --> 41:09.090
A few days later
I'll end up in the hospital again

41:09.090 --> 41:10.420
for malnutrition.

41:11.230 --> 41:14.380
What am I even supposed to eat
at Jin Qiang's?

41:14.900 --> 41:16.870
Nothing suits my appetite there.

41:45.010 --> 41:46.090
I'm going to change my clothes first.

41:46.090 --> 41:47.050
Don't come in.
